.DS_Store
# Claude Code agent state — per-developer, gitignored by default.
# Track only the policy files that document repo-wide conventions:
# `.claude/README.md` (rationale) and `.claude/settings.json` (shared policy
# allowlist, if/when one exists). Per-developer overrides go in
# `settings.local.json` and stay local.
.claude/*
!.claude/README.md
!.claude/settings.json
tmp/
